lead_paragraph: Nothing usually fazes an ice cool Zlatan Ibrahimovic but the Sweden striker was taken aback when he failed to score a penalty during Paris St Germain's 2-2 draw with Manchester City in their Champions League quarter-final first leg on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Ibrahimovic Rues Missed Chances as PSG Held by Man City
headline.main: Ibrahimovic Rues Missed Chances as PSG Held by Man City
